values: This is a TEST campaign!  Anyone reading this is free to edit and play with this spreadsheet to see how it affects the behavior of the coins or calculations.  If you break something, I'll come along at some point and fix it :)  You'll primarily want to scan a coin and watch how it updates the Last Scanned column, "spend" it to see how it changes things, and delete the data to undo/try again.
Light-colored cells with normal font are expecting event host input direct into spreadsheet
Dark-colored cells are automatically calculated or will be updated via Spark-Coin.com
This is an imaginary test coin!  I hope you enjoy exploring this concept!
